node.text:
Cloth diapers are much better for Mother Earth than their disposable counterparts. Since it’s an eco-friendly practice that can easily be done at home, it provides peace of mind for those in our current generation who are more conscious about their environmental footprint than ever before. 
Here, we demonstrate three ways to fold our cloth diapers. Order your pack of cloth diapers today!

node.title: How to Fold a Gerber Cloth Diaper
